sửa dùm 

```dotenv
# ── Meta Ad Library ──────────────────────────────────────────
META_ACCESS_TOKEN=           # Long-lived 60-day token, ads_read permission

APIFY_API_TOKEN=your apify api token


# ── Foreplay ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
FOREPLAY_API_KEY=your foreplay api key
FOREPLAY_EMAIL=your foreplay email
FOREPLAY_PASSWORD=your foreplay password
FOREPLAY_BOARD_ID=           # Optional: auto-save crawled ads to swipe file

# ── AI Models ────────────────────────────────────────────────
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=your anthropic api key
# Whisper transcription: uses faster-whisper (local, free) — no API key needed

# ── Infrastructure ───────────────────────────────────────────
DATABASE_URL=db posgress

REDIS_URL=redis url   # BullMQ / Redis URL

# ── App ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────
NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL=http://localhost:3000


GEMINI_API_KEY=your gemini api key
VIDTORY_API_KEY=your vidtory api key
KIE_API_KEY=your kie api key
ELEVEN_LAB_API_KEY=your eleven lab api key

NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=your supabase url
SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=your supabase service role key
```